Pat Ast https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pat_Ast 0 Pat Ast (October 21, 1941 – October 3, 2001) was an American actress and model. She was best known for starring in Andy Warhol films and being a Halston model and muse in the 1970s. Pat_Ast ( October_21_,_1941 – October_3_,_2001 ) was an_American_actress_and_model .
